---
title: Meatloaf and Mash with Ketchup Glaze, Gravy, and Green Beans
description: These meatloaves have got it. By *it*, we mean that timeless, classic quality that makes this dish as likely to please picky eaters as those with sophisticated tastes. That’s because it’s built around four no-fail, super-satisfying elements: tender ground beef loaves, creamy mashed potatoes, roasted green beans, and a rich gravy. It might just be our biggest crowd-pleaser yet.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/meatloaf-and-mash-7f684371.jpg
